1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:01:00,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.li Support Admin)

2
00:01:30,940 --> 00:01:34,360
[Episode 5]

3
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:36,000
Okay, come on, look over here.

4
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:39,160
Three, two, one, smile.

5
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:40,983
Smile.

6
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,840
You came, too.

7
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,320
Fei, I'll take a couple of photos for you.

8
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,320
Sure, sure, sure!

9
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:54,934
Happy graduation!

10
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:58,120
You're late.

11
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,880
The graduation ceremony is already over.

12
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:01,480
Stop nagging.

13
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:03,800
There's so much to do.

14
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:06,062
Can the graduation ceremony happen again?

15
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,200
I already received my diploma.

16
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:11,720
The principal's gone, too.

17
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:14,960
Then I came here for nothing.

18
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,480
I'll go find the principal.

19
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,760
Wait.

20
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:22,520
I'm already happy that you're here.

21
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,920
I know.

22
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:26,400
I know.

23
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:33,360
Tonight, there's an outdoor movie
at Fortress Square.

24
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,640
Dad and Fei both want to go.

25
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:36,240
Do you want to come along?

26
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,960
What's so good about a free movie?

27
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,640
Are you coming or not?

28
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:45,600
Sure, let's go.

29
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,520
It's all in English.

30
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,960
I can't understand it.

31
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:01,920
No way you'd understand English.

32
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,240
You should ask us college students.

33
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,520
- Dad, let me do it.
- Mr. He!

34
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,720
Let me do it.

35
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:09,400
- Come, take a break.
- Okay.

36
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,640
- Here you go, Dad.
- Isn't this simple?

37
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:12,080
Dad, sit here.

38
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,920
No need, this seat is fine.

39
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,760
This spot is good enough.

40
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:19,200
- Can you handle it?
- It's very simple.

41
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,120
Thanks so much.

42
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,640
Thank you, Fei.

43
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:24,880
No problem at all.

44
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:26,680
Look.

45
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,200
Got it! It's up!

46
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,240
We can watch now.

47
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:32,840
Listen, only I can get the official DVD.

48
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,520
Everyone else is watching pirated copies.

49
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,880
Impressive, right?

50
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:38,240
Amazing! Come on, eat.

51
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,720
You can even use a VCD.

52
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:42,680
- Sit down.
- I want to sit opposite He.

53
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,760
Go ahead, sit down.

54
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:45,600
Thanks.

55
00:03:46,752 --> 00:03:49,990
I can only eat if I can see He.

56
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,680
Here comes the wine.

57
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:56,920
This is my ten-year
brewed bone-strengthening wine.

58
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,880
- Tonight, we drink it.
- Ten years, that's a long time.

59
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:02,280
It contains many precious Chinese herbs.

60
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:04,680
In short, it's very nourishing.

61
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,480
It must taste great.

62
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:08,160
You must savor it, really savor it.

63
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,680
Yes, and here are my meatballs.

64
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:12,640
It's amazing, excellent! Come on, dig in!

65
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:15,280
Today is a good day.

66
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,320
Yes.

67
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:18,040
Let me say a few words first.

68
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,400
Chu San.

69
00:04:20,400 --> 00:04:23,760
Dad is lucky to have a son like you.

70
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:25,680
You haven't had wine before.

71
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,960
Just have a sip.

72
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:30,720
I'll down this cup here.

73
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,520
Then I'll drink, too.

74
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:42,600
Chu San, I wish you a smooth career
and lots of happiness.

75
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:45,040
Most importantly, good health.

76
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:47,760
You don't have to drink. I'll drink.

77
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,320
Fei can really hold his liquor.

78
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:52,640
Then I'll drink, too. Thanks, Fei.

79
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:59,480
Have a cup with me, too.

80
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:03,120
Forget it, just watch the movie.

81
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,880
Why not?

82
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:07,200
You, Mr. He, and Fei all drank.

83
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:09,640
But not with me. Don't care about me, huh?

84
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,160
Then come on.

85
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:17,800
Drink up.

86
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,840
I'm watching you.

87
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:31,400
Come, dig in.

88
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:33,160
This movie is pretty good.

89
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:35,080
Of course it's good.

90
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:49,720
The bride looks beautiful with a veil.

91
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,200
Yes!

92
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:54,120
She's so fair and clean, like a fairy.

93
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,960
You're not bad either.

94
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:57,800
I really like Marlon Brando.

95
00:05:57,800 --> 00:06:00,400
Why is he called Brandy?

96
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:02,000
It sounds like a liquor.

97
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:04,760
It's Brando, Fei.

98
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:06,800
Brando.

99
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,880
Is it Brando or Brandy?

100
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:11,080
Who's Brando?

101
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,400
Gosh!

102
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,960
Fei!

103
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,640
Look at them.

104
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:23,360
You're injured?

105
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,680
No.

106
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,360
There's no injury.

107
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:35,160
Try this.

108
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,560
Okay, fine.

109
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:22,057
Xiao Liu, come to Qi's place.

110
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,960
Do you like it?

111
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:10,160
Yes, I do.

112
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:28,800
♪ Did you wait patiently? ♪

113
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:32,880
♪ Still waiting, waiting to be missed ♪

114
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:35,920
♪ Please don't be afraid ♪

115
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:37,416
Xia Liu Yi.

116
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:41,800
You seem really happy today.

117
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:51,760
I have a place where I feel safe.

118
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,560
And that makes me really happy.

119
00:09:59,986 --> 00:10:02,106
Then you can...

120
00:10:03,133 --> 00:10:05,493
live here forever.

121
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:20,120
Okay.

122
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:54,466
Can I have a bite?

123
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:00,360
Give it to me.

124
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,280
He Chu San.

125
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:34,475
Do you like lollipops that much?

126
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:39,600
No.

127
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:47,000
He Chu San.

128
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,680
Xia Liu Yi.

129
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:21,800
How could I have such a dream?

130
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:32,720
Give me a bite.

131
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:35,160
Give me a bite!

132
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:40,920
If you want it, go get it yourself.

133
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:42,960
There's none left.

134
00:15:28,640 --> 00:15:29,640
Chu San.

135
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:31,680
Why are you up so early?

136
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:34,320
Dad.

137
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:37,640
Why are you washing sheets in the morning?

138
00:15:37,640 --> 00:15:39,760
Last night... I...

139
00:15:42,080 --> 00:15:44,640
Was it because of my wine?

140
00:15:44,640 --> 00:15:47,120
Men of this age...

141
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:49,000
Dad.

142
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,120
Hurry up and cook.

143
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,800
Okay, you keep washing.

144
00:15:51,800 --> 00:15:54,640
I'll make breakfast for you and Mr. Xia.

145
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:12,640
Good morning, Mr. He.
Good morning.

146
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:14,920
He Chu San.

147
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:17,560
Why take my blanket?

148
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:20,360
He dirtied the blanket yesterday

149
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:23,040
and was already washing it early this morning.

150
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:25,480
- You caught a cold?
- Do you get cold easily?

151
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:27,520
You'll get a cold
if you don't cover up in summer.

152
00:16:27,520 --> 00:16:29,640
Hey, He Chu San...

153
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:35,280
Have you brushed your teeth?

154
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:36,480
The toothpaste and brush are over there.

155
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:37,480
Go brush your teeth.

156
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:39,960
Hurry up. Go on.

157
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,160
Chu San.

158
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:49,920
You guys eat first. I'm going to find Fei.

159
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:57,960
The past feels like a fleeting dream,
and it's hard to recognize my feelings...

160
00:16:57,960 --> 00:17:02,480
Why do we bury our old names
after a hundred trials and reunions?

161
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:04,040
He Chu San.

162
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:07,120
Are Mr. He and Fei getting it on?

163
00:17:08,800 --> 00:17:10,040
You're the boss of a gang.

164
00:17:10,040 --> 00:17:12,000
Why are you so gossipy?

165
00:17:15,520 --> 00:17:17,547
He Chu San.

166
00:17:18,926 --> 00:17:21,591
I ask you, but you don't answer me.

167
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:43,629
He Chu San, you're done for.

168
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:56,520
Do you know how to play pool?

169
00:17:56,520 --> 00:17:57,920
No.

170
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:02,360
My company is near yours.

171
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:05,000
Come play pool with me after work.

172
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,280
No way.

173
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:11,520
You idiot.

174
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:15,920
What's going on with you today?

175
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:17,520
You keep saying no to everything.

176
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,960
Xia Liu Yi.

177
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:40,720
Let's keep our distance.

178
00:18:42,120 --> 00:18:44,040
What's wrong with you?

179
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:49,880
Crazy.

180
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:56,000
Xia Liu Yi.

181
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:58,160
Is your phone just for show?

182
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,360
I called you so many times.

183
00:18:59,360 --> 00:19:03,162
If you still don't pick up,
I'll sell Xiaoqi Hall and run away.

184
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:08,280
I left it at He Chu San's place.

185
00:19:10,480 --> 00:19:13,680
Looks like he doesn't want to be your lackey.

186
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:17,149
More like you want to become
the live-in son-in-law of the He Family Clinic.

187
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:22,080
Yesterday at the Sha family gang's dock,

188
00:19:22,080 --> 00:19:24,640
their boss was making a deal
with some Burmese guys,

189
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:26,000
and the Organized Crime Bureau
wiped them out in one go.

190
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,680
They were caught red-handed.

191
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:30,360
Our people at the dock
and the informants in the police

192
00:19:30,360 --> 00:19:32,680
didn't get any news at all.

193
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:34,480
What?

194
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:36,560
It might already be on the news by now.

195
00:19:39,080 --> 00:19:40,480
This is a special report.

196
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:42,320
The Organized Crime Bureau
and the Narcotics Division

197
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:45,000
launched a joint flash operation
early this morning.

198
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:47,120
Under the command of Inspector Xie Jia Hua,

199
00:19:47,120 --> 00:19:48,120
they successfully dismantled

200
00:19:48,120 --> 00:19:50,360
a drug trafficking syndicate that had operated
on Hong Kong Island for many years.

201
00:19:50,360 --> 00:19:53,240
It is reported that Inspector Xie
comes from a police family.

202
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:56,240
His father, Xie Ying Jie,
serves as Deputy Commissioner of Police.

203
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:01,560
This Xie Jia Hua is 31 years old.

204
00:20:01,560 --> 00:20:04,920
He earned a master's degree
in criminal psychology in the U.S.

205
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:07,040
He returned to Hong Kong last August
after completing his studies.

206
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:08,760
Studied in the U.S., huh.

207
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:12,360
He Chu San is pretty smart, too.

208
00:20:12,360 --> 00:20:15,480
Xia Liu Yi, are you even listening to me?

209
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:17,960
Yeah, I hear you. I'm listening.

210
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:20,480
He's just some young master
from the Xie family.

211
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:23,480
Now that he's on TV, he thinks he's a star.

212
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:25,160
With the police making such a big move,

213
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:28,000
they'll definitely come after us next.

214
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,160
What should we do?

215
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:32,480
Every year, we give Inspector Hua
so many red envelopes.

216
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:34,720
If you ask me what we should do,

217
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:37,320
I'd go straight to Inspector Hua's house

218
00:20:37,320 --> 00:20:39,760
and make him spit the money back out.

219
00:20:39,760 --> 00:20:41,800
So, you mean...

220
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:42,800
Xiao Ma.

221
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:46,040
Boss, the men are ready.

222
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:47,160
They're ready to move anytime.

223
00:20:47,160 --> 00:20:48,880
No need to go.

224
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:50,280
Let Fei Qi off this time.

225
00:20:50,280 --> 00:20:52,967
Tell the boys not to act so recklessly for now.

226
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:56,480
- All right.
- Wait.

227
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:57,948
What's going on?

228
00:20:57,948 --> 00:21:00,280
Yesterday, Boss went to Hung Hom

229
00:21:00,280 --> 00:21:02,240
and was chased by Fei Qi's men.

230
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:04,480
Boss told us to smash two of his shops

231
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:06,520
to teach him a lesson.

232
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:07,760
But he's called it off now.

233
00:21:07,760 --> 00:21:10,880
Xia Liu Yi, why did you
go to Fei Qi's turf alone?

234
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:12,800
Looking for your grave?

235
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:15,960
It was He Chu San's graduation ceremony.

236
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:17,480
Fei Qi's guys happened to tail me,

237
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:19,600
and I almost didn't make it in time.

238
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:21,680
All right.

239
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:23,480
I'm sitting here just fine today.

240
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:25,400
A loser like Fei Qi can't keep up with me.

241
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:28,520
You lousy hall master.

242
00:21:28,520 --> 00:21:30,080
Whoever wants the job can have it.

243
00:21:30,080 --> 00:21:31,240
I'm done with it.

244
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:34,282
And this damn mobile phone still needs fixing.

245
00:21:35,240 --> 00:21:37,320
Boss, then the position of hall master...

246
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:40,280
Keep dreaming. She'll come back.

247
00:21:42,080 --> 00:21:43,960
All right.

248
00:21:43,960 --> 00:21:45,720
Stop.

249
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:48,800
Boss, any other orders?

250
00:21:56,600 --> 00:21:58,760
You've been with me for eight years.

251
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:05,920
I remember the first time I met you,

252
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:07,280
it was at Ganglong.

253
00:22:07,280 --> 00:22:08,680
Yeah.

254
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:10,920
I was almost beaten to death back then.

255
00:22:10,920 --> 00:22:12,880
You saved me.

256
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:14,560
Saved your life.

257
00:22:19,840 --> 00:22:22,200
I saved him, too. So, why can't it work?

258
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,600
What's the issue?

259
00:22:25,600 --> 00:22:27,240
Why won't he be my lackey?

260
00:22:27,240 --> 00:22:31,400
I really can't figure out
what He Chu San is thinking.

261
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:32,720
He's just a student.

262
00:22:32,720 --> 00:22:35,320
Boss, why take such a weakling as a lackey?

263
00:22:35,320 --> 00:22:37,440
He can't fight, can't curse.

264
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:45,480
Miss, your drink.

265
00:22:46,280 --> 00:22:47,885
I heard about it.

266
00:22:49,360 --> 00:22:50,360
Thank you.

267
00:22:50,360 --> 00:22:52,480
- Young and promising.
- Go say hello.

268
00:22:53,480 --> 00:22:54,520
Is that him?

269
00:22:54,520 --> 00:22:56,880
Xie is one of the police force's elites.

270
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:58,880
His future is limitless.

271
00:22:58,880 --> 00:23:00,040
It's part of my job.

272
00:23:00,040 --> 00:23:02,640
Inspector Xie is the youngest
Senior Superintendent in history.

273
00:23:02,640 --> 00:23:04,320
Inspector Xie's son is really impressive.

274
00:23:04,320 --> 00:23:05,760
Young and promising.

275
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:07,400
Thank you, thank you.

276
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:10,640
Hua.

277
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:12,480
- Inspector Hua.
- Inspector Hua, you're here.

278
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,480
You don't recognize me?

279
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:15,200
I'm Uncle Hua.

280
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:17,400
You've grown up so much.

281
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:19,720
I still remember over twenty years ago,

282
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:20,920
I was at his first birthday party.

283
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,840
He didn't even look at
all the things on the table,

284
00:23:22,840 --> 00:23:27,480
but he grabbed his father's
police badge right away.

285
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:29,000
- Impressive.
- Yeah.

286
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:33,760
That was when I knew
this kid was born to be a cop.

287
00:23:33,760 --> 00:23:37,160
This is what you call young and promising.

288
00:23:38,160 --> 00:23:40,240
After he returned to the country
and took office,

289
00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:45,560
he immediately took down
the most troublesome drug dealer in Kowloon.

290
00:23:45,560 --> 00:23:47,400
Impressive.

291
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:50,480
You're wasting your talent
staying in the Organized Crime Bureau.

292
00:23:50,480 --> 00:23:53,400
Soon, I'll be transferred to Kowloon West.

293
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:55,480
District Superintendent.

294
00:23:55,480 --> 00:23:59,560
I'll save the Assistant Superintendent
position for you.

295
00:23:59,560 --> 00:24:02,200
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

296
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:04,480
- Congratulations.
- Chief Superintendent Hua.

297
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:08,040
I'd think the Kowloon West District
is your family's business.

298
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:10,800
Personnel transfers must follow the rules.

299
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:12,600
We're police officers.

300
00:24:12,600 --> 00:24:14,560
We must uphold the law.

301
00:24:14,560 --> 00:24:17,560
And we certainly can't steal from within.

302
00:24:18,560 --> 00:24:20,240
Come on, cheers.

303
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:22,640
Let's drink.

304
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:24,200
Hello, sir.

305
00:24:27,560 --> 00:24:30,320
Congratulations, Hua.

306
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:33,160
Dad, you're here.

307
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:35,360
Hua, you're looking very impressive today.

308
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:38,600
Congratulations.

309
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:41,400
Don't worry about me today.

310
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:44,080
I'm just here as James' dad.

311
00:24:44,080 --> 00:24:45,920
Enjoy yourselves.

312
00:24:48,080 --> 00:24:49,680
Let's sit over there.

313
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:52,200
Thank you.

314
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:55,960
Dad.

315
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:57,120
You're so busy.

316
00:24:57,120 --> 00:24:59,960
You didn't need to make
a special trip for this small case.

317
00:24:59,960 --> 00:25:01,800
What small case?

318
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:03,480
The drug lord who's been a menace for years,

319
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:04,840
and the whole drug trafficking network.

320
00:25:04,840 --> 00:25:07,480
Your dad's been a cop his whole life,

321
00:25:07,480 --> 00:25:11,840
and hasn't handled many cases as neat as this.

322
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:17,800
By the way, were you injured on this mission?

323
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:19,040
No.

324
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:21,840
You've got a wound on your neck.

325
00:25:25,766 --> 00:25:27,166
It's an allergy.

326
00:25:32,880 --> 00:25:37,080
I knew it, you can't take care of yourself.

327
00:25:37,080 --> 00:25:39,120
- Huang's daughter...
- Dad.

328
00:25:39,120 --> 00:25:40,560
I just want to be like you,

329
00:25:40,560 --> 00:25:42,400
and be an outstanding police officer.

330
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:44,480
To fight evil, protect the good,
and uphold justice.

331
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:46,920
But you can't just focus on work.

332
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:48,600
It's time.

333
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:50,160
Got it.

334
00:26:07,120 --> 00:26:08,680
Excuse me.

335
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:34,682
Are you the Deputy Commissioner
of Police, Xie Ying Jie?

336
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,400
That's me.

337
00:26:38,120 --> 00:26:39,560
Hello.

338
00:26:40,480 --> 00:26:41,800
My name is Lu Guang Ming.

339
00:26:41,800 --> 00:26:43,160
I've just joined the Independent Commission
Against Corruption.

340
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:44,800
I'm an Assistant Investigator.

341
00:26:44,800 --> 00:26:46,400
You've been my idol since I was young.

342
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:49,360
Your integrity inspired me
to pursue a career in law enforcement.

343
00:26:49,360 --> 00:26:51,720
Thank you, you're too kind.

344
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:55,320
Can I sit down and chat with you?

345
00:26:55,320 --> 00:26:56,800
No.

346
00:26:59,280 --> 00:27:00,840
Hua.

347
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:03,400
Sorry about that.

348
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:05,680
Jia Hua is a little introverted.

349
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:07,080
He doesn't have many friends.

350
00:27:07,080 --> 00:27:10,080
Most of the people here today
are his colleagues.

351
00:27:10,080 --> 00:27:13,960
I didn't even know he had friends here.

352
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:16,520
I've only just met Jia Hua recently.

353
00:27:16,520 --> 00:27:19,320
He's taught me a lot.

354
00:27:20,080 --> 00:27:23,040
Right, Jia Hua?

355
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:31,520
Sir, the car is here.

356
00:27:31,520 --> 00:27:34,760
I'd love to chat more with you,

357
00:27:34,760 --> 00:27:37,160
but I have to leave now.

358
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:38,840
You guys carry on.

359
00:27:38,840 --> 00:27:42,680
By the way, since you're Jia Hua's friend,

360
00:27:43,440 --> 00:27:44,520
feel free to come by anytime.

361
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:46,290
[Xie Ying Jie]

362
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:49,920
Definitely.

363
00:28:10,760 --> 00:28:12,000
What are you doing?

364
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:13,280
Why are you here?

365
00:28:13,280 --> 00:28:14,720
Who are you?

366
00:28:21,080 --> 00:28:22,520
Inspector Xie.

367
00:28:22,520 --> 00:28:24,320
Take it easy.

368
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:27,880
I just started working,
and my salary isn't high.

369
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:30,080
It's not easy to buy a decent suit.

370
00:28:30,080 --> 00:28:32,120
Answer my question.

371
00:28:33,760 --> 00:28:35,480
Lu Guang Ming.

372
00:28:36,760 --> 00:28:39,280
Assistant Investigator of
the Independent Commission Against Corruption.

373
00:28:39,280 --> 00:28:40,640
Today, I'm here on behalf of the ICAC

374
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:43,360
to attend the Outstanding Case Seminar.

375
00:28:48,520 --> 00:28:51,400
You just gave a speech on stage.

376
00:28:53,080 --> 00:28:55,440
I wrote everything down.

377
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:57,240
Not a word missed.

378
00:28:57,240 --> 00:28:59,480
Every word was brilliant.

379
00:29:04,360 --> 00:29:06,440
You deliberately got close to me last night.

380
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:08,560
Inspector Xie.

381
00:29:08,560 --> 00:29:10,640
You can't just say anything.

382
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:12,760
There are so many gay bars down in Central.

383
00:29:12,760 --> 00:29:15,880
Who doesn't hide their true self?

384
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:19,760
You don't want anyone to know
about last night, do you?

385
00:29:21,080 --> 00:29:24,400
I saw you speaking on stage today

386
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:28,960
and that was when I realized
how destined we are.

387
00:29:31,800 --> 00:29:34,600
Have you told anyone about us?

388
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:50,400
What are you talking about?

389
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:56,040
All right.

390
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:59,960
We just ran into each other last night.

391
00:30:00,960 --> 00:30:03,560
A one-night stand.

392
00:30:03,560 --> 00:30:05,560
But Inspector Xie...

393
00:30:07,800 --> 00:30:11,840
Last night, I thought we both
had feelings for each other.

394
00:30:12,760 --> 00:30:17,040
But you treated me
like a prostitute for 163 bucks.

395
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:22,200
Isn't that a little cheap for a prostitute?

396
00:30:24,800 --> 00:30:26,880
I was drunk last night.

397
00:30:31,080 --> 00:30:33,200
I was drunk last night.

398
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:36,920
I only had that much on me.

399
00:30:36,920 --> 00:30:38,560
It's fine.

400
00:30:39,280 --> 00:30:41,680
I'll take care of it myself.

401
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:47,000
I really have to thank you.

402
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:49,920
How else would a big shot like your father

403
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:52,920
give his business card to someone like me?

404
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:55,400
You came because of my father.

405
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:59,200
Inspector Xie, last night...

406
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:03,000
it seemed like you asked me
to have a drink first.

407
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:05,760
I didn't ask you for your ID.

408
00:31:10,080 --> 00:31:11,920
All right.

409
00:31:11,920 --> 00:31:14,320
Don't worry.

410
00:31:14,320 --> 00:31:18,080
I won't tell anyone about this.

411
00:31:18,080 --> 00:31:23,080
That wouldn't be good for you or me.

412
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:32,200
Let's get to the point.

413
00:31:36,360 --> 00:31:39,200
I've been working with a detective recently.

414
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:43,680
I suspect he's involved with
the drug case you just cracked.

415
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:45,480
I want...

416
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:49,560
all the information on this case.

417
00:31:52,440 --> 00:31:54,800
The drug case is classified.

418
00:31:54,800 --> 00:31:57,080
Many of the related forces
are still on the loose.

419
00:31:57,080 --> 00:31:58,760
I can't give it to you.

420
00:31:58,760 --> 00:32:00,760
If you want to investigate,

421
00:32:00,760 --> 00:32:02,760
give me the information you have.

422
00:32:02,760 --> 00:32:04,800
I'll look into it along with the drug case.

423
00:32:04,800 --> 00:32:08,160
If it's really like you said,
I won't let him go.

424
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:09,160
Okay?

425
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:11,360
No, Inspector Xie.

426
00:32:12,320 --> 00:32:14,920
Someone like me had no resources,

427
00:32:14,920 --> 00:32:18,800
no background, no connections.

428
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:21,920
It's not that easy to investigate a case.

429
00:32:21,920 --> 00:32:25,880
I'm counting on this case to get promoted.

430
00:32:28,800 --> 00:32:31,120
You don't want to investigate the case.

431
00:32:31,120 --> 00:32:32,880
You want to use my information

432
00:32:32,880 --> 00:32:35,320
to make it your leverage.

433
00:32:35,320 --> 00:32:37,040
In simple terms,

434
00:32:37,040 --> 00:32:40,480
you're trying to use me and climb the ranks.

435
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:43,000
Inspector Xie.

436
00:32:43,760 --> 00:32:46,600
Someone like you, born under a lucky star,

437
00:32:46,600 --> 00:32:51,760
would never understand ordinary people like us.

438
00:32:51,760 --> 00:32:54,200
Listen, from now on,

439
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:55,440
we have nothing to do with each other.

440
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:58,200
Please keep last night's encounter to yourself.

441
00:32:58,200 --> 00:33:00,360
I'll act like it never happened.

442
00:33:05,280 --> 00:33:07,240
One more thing.

443
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:09,840
Don't think you can use my position
for personal gain.

444
00:33:09,840 --> 00:33:11,400
I hate people like you the most.

445
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:12,840
Inspector Xie.

446
00:33:12,840 --> 00:33:16,000
Please make sure to investigate
Senior Inspector Hua in Kowloon.

447
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:20,600
If you get any information,
please tell me immediately.

448
00:33:20,600 --> 00:33:23,600
If you need me, I will always be...

449
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:26,533
here.

450
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:48,880
Are you Senior Inspector Hua of Kowloon?

451
00:33:48,880 --> 00:33:52,040
About the transfer from the Sha family gang
to your daughter,

452
00:33:52,040 --> 00:33:53,880
you'd better come up
with an explanation quickly.

453
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:59,287
Otherwise, I'm afraid you might
compromise your reputation before retirement.

454
00:34:14,320 --> 00:34:17,000
Dad, I'm heading to work.

455
00:34:17,660 --> 00:34:19,040
So handsome.

456
00:34:19,040 --> 00:34:20,280
Wait a second.

457
00:34:21,800 --> 00:34:23,760
All right, good luck.

458
00:34:23,760 --> 00:34:25,120
Thanks.

459
00:34:25,120 --> 00:34:26,400
Come back early.

460
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:27,960
Okay.

461
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:33,120
Hello.

462
00:34:33,120 --> 00:34:35,200
Lily, give him the project ID badge.

463
00:34:35,200 --> 00:34:36,480
Sure.

464
00:34:37,640 --> 00:34:39,360
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

465
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:40,760
This way.

466
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:42,240
Lucy.

467
00:34:44,360 --> 00:34:45,400
This is Sonny.

468
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:48,160
Hello, I'm He Chu San.

469
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:50,460
Call me "Sam".

470
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:53,280
This is Mike.

471
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:54,440
Hello.

472
00:34:54,440 --> 00:34:55,800
This is Pam.

473
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:57,200
This is Mark.

474
00:34:58,560 --> 00:35:00,760
Your seat is here.

475
00:35:00,760 --> 00:35:02,400
- Mine?
- Yes.

476
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:03,760
Work hard.

477
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:05,000
Okay.

478
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:22,320
- Michael.
- All right, thanks.

479
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:24,680
David.

480
00:35:24,680 --> 00:35:26,560
Thanks.

481
00:35:30,120 --> 00:35:31,920
Take a look at him.

482
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:34,240
He's so handsome.

483
00:35:34,240 --> 00:35:35,280
Do you want a bite?

484
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:37,600
No, you eat.

485
00:35:37,600 --> 00:35:39,560
No, thanks.

486
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:50,080
- Is this okay?
- Not bad.

487
00:35:50,080 --> 00:35:52,160
Very handsome.

488
00:35:52,160 --> 00:35:53,240
Sam.

489
00:35:53,240 --> 00:35:55,080
You did a good job on your report today.

490
00:35:55,080 --> 00:35:57,080
The clients all said
you were very professional.

491
00:35:57,080 --> 00:35:58,800
They feel very reassured.

492
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,960
Young man.

493
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:04,360
- Call him over.
- Chu San.

494
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:07,640
What brings you here?

495
00:36:07,640 --> 00:36:10,120
Sam, who are they?

496
00:36:11,080 --> 00:36:13,760
Sir, you are our young man's...

497
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:16,480
Chu San's superior, right?

498
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:18,920
Chu San works here.

499
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:20,680
No one would bully him, right?

500
00:36:20,680 --> 00:36:22,280
Of course not.

501
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:24,080
What are you doing?

502
00:36:24,080 --> 00:36:25,480
Boss wants to talk to you.

503
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:27,760
He sent us to pick you up.

504
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:32,440
Chu San is now in Xiaoqi Hall...

505
00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:34,640
Just kidding.

506
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:37,440
Come on, get in the car.

507
00:36:37,440 --> 00:36:38,560
Get in.

508
00:36:38,560 --> 00:36:39,560
- Drive.
- Let's go.
All right.

509
00:36:40,560 --> 00:36:43,040
Well, feeling flattered?

510
00:37:21,600 --> 00:37:23,200
Boss.

511
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:27,280
What are you doing?

512
00:37:27,280 --> 00:37:30,400
Today's a good day.

513
00:37:31,680 --> 00:37:34,960
I specially arranged
a formal initiation ceremony.

514
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:36,640
In front of Guan Yu,

515
00:37:36,640 --> 00:37:39,680
you pledge me as your big brother today.

516
00:37:39,680 --> 00:37:44,000
From now on, you'll be my brother for life.

517
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:53,560
A brother's promise,

518
00:37:55,120 --> 00:37:57,440
blood spilled across the land.

519
00:37:57,440 --> 00:38:08,320
A brother's promise,
blood spilled across the land.

520
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:11,040
Why did you do all this
without asking me first?

521
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:16,040
Xiao Ma is right.

522
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:21,240
We were too hasty in
making you join Xiaoqi Hall before.

523
00:38:21,240 --> 00:38:25,160
So, this time, I'll handle everything
with the highest standards.

524
00:38:25,160 --> 00:38:26,560
Cheers!

525
00:38:26,560 --> 00:38:28,800
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

526
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:41,760
Cheers! Cheers!

527
00:38:41,760 --> 00:38:43,320
Cheers!

528
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:58,440
I've said it once.

529
00:38:58,440 --> 00:39:00,920
Now, I'll say it again.

530
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:03,080
I, He Chu San,

531
00:39:03,080 --> 00:39:05,760
will never be your underling.

532
00:39:11,640 --> 00:39:13,680
Young man!

533
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:49,116
Are you unhappy?

534
00:39:50,240 --> 00:39:55,240
He Chu San is immune
to both threats and persuasion.

535
00:39:57,120 --> 00:39:58,560
What's wrong?

536
00:39:58,560 --> 00:40:01,080
This time, are you set on getting him?

537
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:05,680
Didn't you say you wouldn't check the accounts?

538
00:40:05,680 --> 00:40:07,400
Aren't I looking for a cultured person?

539
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:11,040
I meant someone cultured like him.

540
00:40:11,040 --> 00:40:13,320
If you really want someone
to be your subordinate,

541
00:40:13,320 --> 00:40:15,040
it's not that easy.

542
00:40:15,040 --> 00:40:17,760
His mother died because of the triads.

543
00:40:23,200 --> 00:40:25,160
What did you say?

544
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:28,760
You didn't know?

545
00:40:30,200 --> 00:40:32,640
He Chu San was adopted.

546
00:40:32,640 --> 00:40:34,800
His real mother was a beautiful woman.

547
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:36,360
She was with a gangster.

548
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:37,760
Right before giving birth to him,

549
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:40,760
his father was hacked to death in the street.

550
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:42,520
His mother gave birth prematurely to him,

551
00:40:42,520 --> 00:40:44,240
and then passed away.

552
00:40:44,240 --> 00:40:46,840
Then Dr. He adopted him.

553
00:40:46,840 --> 00:40:48,760
It's said that just before she died,

554
00:40:48,760 --> 00:40:50,680
her last words were...

555
00:40:50,680 --> 00:40:55,160
"Never let He Chu San
get involved with the triads."
